    "en": {
      "title": "A red notice from the weather",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Meteorological Department has issued a warning about heavy rains. This announcement issued at 7.00 am today will be valid until 7.00 am tomorrow.",
        "According to the Department of Meteorology, very heavy rains of more than 150 mm are expected in some places in the Bawan West, South, Sabaragamuwa, Central and Uva provinces where there is a turbulent situation in the lower atmosphere.",
        "Also, the department adds that heavy rains of around 100 mm may occur in other areas."
      ],
